Mariner Investment Group, LLC


Mariner is powered by significant investing experience and anchored by a strong commitment
to risk management. An investment advisory firm founded in 1992, Mariner specializes in
alternative asset management, providing investment solutions across a broad range of markets
to sophisticated investors.






