Mariner Investment Group, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager which provides advisory services to its clients. The company also has offices in Boston, MA, Harrison, NY, New York, NY, Rowayton, CT, as well as in Gangnam-Gu, Seoul, London, UK, and Minato-Ku, Tokyo.
Mariner Investment Group, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager which provides advisory services to its clients. The company also has offices in Boston, MA, Harrison, NY, New York, NY, Rowayton, CT, as well as in Gangnam-Gu, Seoul, London, UK, and Minato-Ku, Tokyo.

The lean corporate information technology… MoreMariner Investment Group, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager which provides advisory services to its clients. The company also has offices in Boston, MA, Harrison, NY, New York, NY, Rowayton, CT, as well as in Gangnam-Gu, Seoul, London, UK, and Minato-Ku, Tokyo.

The lean corporate information technology department at Mariner Investment Group is responsible for the day-to-day operational support of the company's corporate office in New York, NY, as well as offices around the world. IT staff is responsible for the overall infrastructure support, including telecommunications systems, systems and server administration, desktop support, information security, storage area networking, messaging services, IT help desk, and intra-networking.





