Company Overview of Mariner Investment Group, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mariner Investment Group, LLC is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. It provides its services to privately offered pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations or other businesses, state or municipal government entities endowments, foundations, insurance companies, and plan sponsors. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It invests in the public equity, fixed income markets, and alternative asset markets across the globe. It also provide equity capital for investments. The firm operates as a subsidiary of MIG Holdings, LLC. The firm was previously known as Mariner Investment Group, Inc...
Mariner Investment Group, LLC is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. It provides its services to privately offered pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations or other businesses, state or municipal government entities endowments, foundations, insurance companies, and plan sponsors. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It invests in the public equity, fixed income markets, and alternative asset markets across the globe. It also provide equity capital for investments. The firm operates as a subsidiary of MIG Holdings, LLC. The firm was previously known as Mariner Investment Group, Inc. Mariner Investment Group, LLC was founded in 1992 and is based in New York City with additional offices across North America and Asia.
Detailed Description


485 Madison Avenue22nd FloorNew York, NY 10022United StatesFounded in 1992



