Mariner Investment Group, LLC Key Developments

Mariner Investment Group, LLC Presents at RiskHedge USA 2016, Sep-20-2016 09:30 AM
Sep 16 16
Mariner Investment Group, LLC Presents at RiskHedge USA 2016, Sep-20-2016 09:30 AM. Venue: Manhattan NYC, An Affinia Hotel, 371 7th Avenue, New York, NY 10001, United States. Speakers: Dmitry Green, Chief Risk Officer.


Mariner Investment Group Closes $503 Million Collateralized Loan Obligation
Aug 11 16
Mariner Investment Group announced the closing of a $503 million collateralized loan obligation. This is the third such transaction by Mariner's leveraged credit team and marks a total of approximately $1.5 billion in CLOs they have successfully closed in the past two years. Mariner's leveraged credit team transitioned from ORIX USA, Mariner's parent company, in 2014. The 15-member team is co-led by David Martin and Erik Gunnerson, who together bring over 30 years of combined investment expertise. Martin and Gunnerson have managed the team for nearly seven years including while at ORIX USA and since the group moved to Mariner.


IX Capital Eyes Acquisitions
Mar 22 16
ORIX USA Corporation announced that the formation of IX Capital Partners, a new investment initiative of its majority-owned subsidiary, Mariner Investment Group, LLC. IX Capital Partners - Private Equity is seeking to invest in equity capital in a variety of industries and special situations in North America. 


