Asset Management | ORIX



























Skip to content








Asset Management
ORIX Asset Management (OAM) is the holding company for ORIX’s various asset management businesses and investments.


Mariner Investment Group
Mariner Investment Group, LLC (Mariner) is a New York-based hedge fund manager founded in 1992 with approximately 150 employees and offices in New York, London*, Tokyo, Philadelphia, Dallas, Harrison (NY), Rowayton (CT) and Summit (NJ). Mariner and its associated advisers have over $10 billion in assets under management. ORIX USA owns an indirect majority interest in Mariner with Mariner’s current and former principals owning a substantial minority interest. Mariner is an SEC and CFTC registered investment adviser. Mariner and its affiliates advise several single and multi-strategy hedge funds, funds of funds and offer other alternative investment products and services.  The firm launched a CLO business in 2015 and has closed three funds.
*Denotes a Mariner affiliated office Mariner Investment (Europe) LLP










